latestIgtvVideos.title: Suji chilla & Suji balls.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Suji can be given to babies from 6month.
Start with Suji Serra, Suji plain Upma, Suji plain chilla Add vegetables according to ur choice after 9months. 
Avoid salt & sugar till a year.
(Video has been made when devansh was 1 year+ soo I added bit salt & spices)

latestIgtvVideos.title: Tricolour Suji chilla
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Tried something new for devansh. Tricolour Suji chilla with Suji, carrot, capsicum, coriander. He totally loved it. Must try with your Baby they ll love colourful food.
